cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about improving the transferability of adversarial examples in neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning and computer vision research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves optimizing for adversarial examples, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
